  <summary date="2022-08-19T13:11:51Z" status="Introduced in House">Supplying America Needs Truckers Aged 18 Act or the SANTA 18 Act

This bill exempts drivers who transport goods from a port of entry and another place within the same state from age restrictions and other requirements that apply to federal commercial driver's licenses.</summary>
